dct_description_sm: Reissued in: Atlas manuale ... [Map 35]/by Herman Moll. -- London : Printed for T. Childe and F. Churchil in Pater-Noster-Row in St. Paul's Church-yard, 1713.
Without page numbers or other text.

California as an island with flat northern coast and no place names. Land of Jesso and S. of Vries to northwest, and S. of Annian to north. Western Canada is called New North Wales.Prime Meridian: [Tenerife].
